net.futuredrama.circleprogressbar.circleprogressbar

Class CircleProgressBarView

  • java.lang.Object
    • View
      • net.futuredrama.circleprogressbar.circleprogressbar.CircleProgressBarView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BarAnimationListener

    public class CircleProgressBarView
extends View
implements BarAnimationListener
    A subclass of View class for creating a circular progressBar. The progressbar will display the progress of a number of BarComponent that has been added to it.
